longBusinessSummary: Profarma Distribuidora de Produtos Farmacêuticos S.A., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the distribution and retail sale of pharmaceutical products in Brazil. The company operates through two segments, Distribution and Retail segments. It provides medicines, human drugs, personal hygiene, veterinary, perfumery, and cosmetic and beauty products. The company operates retail stores under the Drogasmil, Farmalife, Tamoio, and Rede Rosário brands. Profarma Distribuidora de Produtos Farmacêuticos S.A. was incorporated in 1961 and is headquartered in Rio De Janeiro, Brazil.
